high_descs: Turn to the left and walk to face the countertop that is to the left of the sink.
Pick up the fork that is to the left of the spoon from the white countertop.
Walk to the right until you are directly in front of the sink.
Place the fork into the sink, turn on the water, turn off the water, and remove the fork.
Walk to the left until you are standing in front of the small dark table with three shelves.
Place the fork on top of the dark wood table that is to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed fork onto the dark wood table.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick the fork up from the counter.
Move to the right and face the sink.
Put the fork in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the fork up again.
Move to the left and face the small black table to the left of the counter.
Put the fork down on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter on the left side of the sink.
Pick up the fork on the counter.
Wash the fork in the sink.
Place the fork on the black table to the right of the front salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean fork on a table.
